Ikklisiya biyu an gina su ne daga majami'u na fararen fata kafin Harlem ta zama birni mai birni mai birni a 1870, kuma St. Martin's a cikin shekaru goma bayan haka.
Ƙungiyar Methodist na farko ta ƙaura a shekara ta 1930.
Ikilisiyar 'yan baƙar fata da ke yin addininsu a kusa da wurin suna mallakar ginin.
St. Martin's ya karbe shi daga ikilisiyar baƙar fata a lokacin mulkin Fasto John Howard Johnson, wanda ya jagoranci yajin aikin dillalai a kan 125th Street, babban hanyar cin kasuwa a Harlem, wanda ya ƙi yin aiki ko haɓaka baƙar fata.
An lalata ginin sosai a cikin wuta a 1939, amma saboda membobin Ikilisiyar Uba Johnson suna da shirin sake gina shi, sun sayi carillon.
Fada David Johnson, ɗan mahaifin Johnson kuma magajin St. Martin, ya yi alfahari da kiran karlon "ƙwanƙolin matalauta".
Masanin da ke wasa da karillon a watan Yuli ya kira shi daban: "dukiya ta al'adu" da "kayan tarihi mara canji".
Masanin, Tiffany Ng daga Jami'ar Michigan, ya kuma lura cewa wannan shi ne karlon na farko a duniya da wani ɗan baƙar fata mai suna Dionysio A. Lind ya yi, wanda ya koma babban karlon a wani coci a Riverside shekaru 18 da suka gabata.
Mista Meriwether ya ce St. Martin bai maye gurbinsa ba.
