Ma'aurata suna hutu tare kuma Jones yana da kashi 40% na kamfanin samar da talabijin na Baldwin.
Willoughby ya kamata ya zama jakadan M&S kuma ya maye gurbin Ant McPartlin a matsayin mai gabatar da Ni Celebrity na ITV.
