Mutane fiye da miliyan 20 ne suka kalli jawabin Brad Kavanaugh
Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli shaidar da aka bayar a ranar Alhamis ta mai neman kujerar kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh, da matar da ta zarge shi da laifin cin zarafin da ake zargin ya faru ne a shekarun 1980s, Christina Blassy Ford, a tashoshin talabijin shida.
A halin yanzu, halin da ake ciki na siyasa ya ci gaba, tare da masu magana da yawun da suka katse shirye-shiryen juyin juya halin na yau da kullun a ranar Juma'a: Jeff Flake, Sanata daga Arizona, ya kulla yarjejeniya da FBI don gudanar da binciken mako guda game da tuhumar.
Ford ta gaya wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa cewa ta tabbata cewa Kavanaugh ya sace piano kuma ya yi kokarin cire tufafinta a wata liyafa ta makarantar sakandare.
Kavanaugh, a cikin shaidar da ya bayar, ya ce yana da tabbacin cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Wataƙila sama da mutane miliyan 20.4, kamar yadda Nielsen ta ruwaito, sun kalli shi a ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin ya ƙididdige yawan kallon CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a nan da nan aka samu lambobin sauran hanyoyin da suka nuna shi ba, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Kuma Nielsen yawanci yana da matsala wajen auna mutane da suke kallo a ofisoshi.
Don a kwatanta shi da kyau, wannan jama'a ce da take da girma kamar wasan ƙwallon ƙafa ko kuma kyautar fim.
Kamfanin Fox News, wanda masu gudanar da shi suka yi ta kai hari kan nadin Kavanaugh, ya yi fice a kan dukkan cibiyoyin da suka kalli matsakaicin masu sauraro miliyan 5.69 a lokacin sauraron sauraron, in ji Nielsen.
ABC ce ta biyu da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS tana da miliyan 3.1 da NBC tana da miliyan 2.94 da MSNBC tana da miliyan 2.89 da CNN tana da miliyan 2.52, in ji Nielsen.
An ci gaba da samun karɓan saƙo bayan an yi wa'azin.
