Bayan da ofishin 'yan adawar suka sanar da cewa zai zabi Kavanaugh, kyamarorin CNN da CBS sun kama masu zanga-zanga suna kiransa a safiyar Juma'a yayin da yake kokarin shiga lif don sauraron kwamitin shari'a.
Ya tsaya tare da idanunsa a rufe na mintuna da dama yayin da ake yi masa tambayoyi, kuma an watsa shi kai tsaye a CNN.
