Tashar YouTube don taron Trump a West Virginia
Shugaba Donald Trump ya kaddamar da wani gangamin gangamin yakin neman zabe a garin Willing, na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko cikin tarurrukan Trump biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da ziyarar zuwa wurare masu nisa kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da aka yi zaben tabbatar da zabensa na cike wa babban kotun kasar da ya ɓace, Trump yana kokarin gina goyon baya ga zaben da za a yi a tsakiyar shekara, saboda 'yan Republican na iya rasa iko a majalisa a zaben na watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump zai gudana a yammacin Virginia kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon sa a kan intanet?
An shirya taron Trump a Willing, West Virginia da karfe 7 na yamma, a yankin gabas da yamma, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a kan layi ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
A wannan makon, mai yiwuwa Trump zai yi jawabi a zaman sauraron wanda ya zaba a matsayin babban alkalin kotun, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya zama mai cike da tashin hankali game da zargin cin zarafin jima'i, inda ake sa ran jinkirta zaben majalisar dattawa har zuwa mako guda, yayin da ake ci gaba da binciken FBI.
Babban manufar jerin tarurrukan shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican su sami nasara a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Saboda haka, kamfen din shugaban kasa Trump ya ce wadannan tarurruka biyar na mako mai zuwa na nufin "karfafawa masu aikin sa kai da masu goyon baya" yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da kuma majalisar wakilai, a cewar Reuters.
"Samun iko a majalisa na da muhimmanci a ajandar shugaban kasa, don haka zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama a lokacin fara yakin neman zabe", in ji wani mai magana da yawun Trump, wanda ya ki bayyana sunansa.
An shirya taron a filin wasa na Wesbanco a Willing, da yammacin yau ana iya samun masu goyon baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, da kuma kafofin watsa labarai daga Pittsburgh, a cewar Metro News daga West Virginia.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump ya kai ziyara karo na biyu a West Virginia a cikin wata daya, jihar da ya lashe zaben da ya kai kashi 40 a 2016.
Trump na kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar Senate na jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, wanda ke bin bayan zaben.
"Ba shi da kyau ga Morrissey cewa shugaban ya zo don inganta ƙuri'un", in ji Simon Heather, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
