HIV/AIDS: China ta ruwaito karuwar sabbin kamuwa da cutar da kashi 14 cikin 100
Kasar Sin ta sanar da karuwar mutane 14 cikin 100 da ke da cutar HIV da kuma cutar AIDS.
Fiye da mutane 820,000 ne ke fama da cutar a kasar, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya.
An samu sabbin mutane 40,000 a kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai.
Yawancin sababbin abubuwan da suka faru sun kasance ta hanyar jima'i, wanda shine canji daga baya.
A al'adance, cutar HIV ta yadu cikin sauri a sassan kasar Sin sakamakon kamuwa da jini.
Amma adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan sifili, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Amma duk da haka, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a ƙasar Sin yana ƙaruwa da mutane 100,000 a kowace shekara.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i ta zama babbar matsala ga al'ummar LGBT a kasar Sin.
An yi wa luwadi yancin yin aiki a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma ana nuna wa mutanen LGBT nuna wariya sosai.
Domin ra'ayin da ya dace da al'adun ƙasar, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70-90 na mazajen da suke yin jima'i da maza za su auri mata.
Yawancin cututtuka na cutar suna faruwa ne saboda rashin kāriya ta jima'i a cikin waɗannan alaƙar.
Tun 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da maganin cutar HIV ga kowa a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
