Tunani game da Johnny English ya sake kai hari - ya lalata yaudarar leken asiri na Rowan Atkinson
Yanzu al'ada ce a nemi abubuwan Brexit a kowane sabon fim na Burtaniya, kuma hakan na iya kasancewa gaskiya ga wannan sabuntawar ta cinikin cinikin cinikin Johnny English - wanda ya fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma ya sake maimaita shi a 2011 tare da Johnny English: Sake Haihuwa.
Shin yin dariya da kanmu game da yadda muke bayyana a ko'ina zai zama sabon damar fitar da kayayyaki ga al'ummarmu?
Duk da haka, mai girma idanu da kuma mutane da yawa grimaces na m Johnny Turanci samu lasisi don "sanya abubuwa a karo na biyu" - sunansa farko da ya nuna cewa shi ne mai fadi-sikelin comic halittar, sanya ga masu kallo a cinema a kasashen da ba a magana da harshen Turanci.
Tabbas, yana da wani ɗan ɗan ɗan leƙen asiri wanda duk da ƙoƙarinsa na ban mamaki na yin kyan gani, ya ɗan yi kama da Clouseau, yana da siffofin Mr. Bean, da kuma wani ɓangare na saurayin da ke buga waƙa daga waƙar Wasan wuta daga bikin buɗe wasannin Olympics na London na 2012.
Tushen shi ne matafiyi kuma mai ban mamaki na duniya Atkinson wanda ya taɓa yin fim a cikin tallan TV na Barclays da aka manta yanzu, yana barin rikici a bayansa.
Akwai wani abu ko biyu a cikin sabon littafin Johnny English.
Abin da na fi so shi ne lokacin da Johnny English yake zuwa wurin wani jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu da ya saka makamai masu linzami na zamanin da, kuma yana da ƙwanƙwasawa a kan kwalkwali.
Ana iya ganin baiwar Atkinson na wasan kwaikwayo na zahiri, amma abin dariya yana da rauni kuma yana da ɗan taushi, musamman tunda alamun fim ɗin "mai tsanani" kamar 007 da Mission: Impossible da kansu suna da abubuwan wasan kwaikwayo.
Abin dariya kamar an tsara shi ne don yara maimakon manya, kuma a wurina, hatsarin Johnny English ba shi da ƙwarewa da kuma maida hankali kamar yadda ake yin shiru na mutumin Atkinson, Bean.
Maganar da ake ta yi a kullum ita ce, Birtaniya na cikin matsala.
Wani dan leken asiri ya shiga cikin wani babban asirin 'yan leken asiri na Birtaniya, ya bayyana sunayen duk wani dan Birtaniya da ke kan hanya, abin takaici ga dan leken asirin da ke kan aiki - wani dan takaici ga Kevin Eldon.
A karshe dama ga firaminista wanda yake da ban mamaki da kuma fadaci hali kuma riga shan wahala daga cikakken m na siyasa unpopularity: Emma Thompson da aka ba da kansa a cikin wannan hali na kwasa-kwasan Theresa May, amma babu wani abu na musamman a cikin rubutun da za a yi aiki tare da.
Masu ba ta shawara a kan harkokin tsaro sun gaya mata cewa tun da yake an yi wa kowane ɗan leƙen asiri barazana, za ta bukaci ta sa ɗaya daga cikin 'yan gudun hijirar ya yi aiki.
Kuma wannan yana nufin kiran Johnny English da kansa wanda yanzu yake aiki a matsayin malami a wata makaranta mai zaman kanta, amma yana koyar da darussan ɓoye ɓoye: akwai wasu kyawawan yara a nan, lokacin da Inglish ke ba da makarantar leken asiri wanda ke kama da makarantar rock.
An kira Ingilishi da sauri zuwa White Hall don gaggawa kuma an sake haɗuwa da tsohon abokin aikinsa Bow, wanda ke wasa da Ben Miller.
Bow yanzu ya yi aure, yana da dangantaka da kwamandan jirgin ruwa, wani rawar da Vicky Pepperdine ba ta yi amfani da shi ba.
To, Batman da Robin, don su lalata duk abin da ke cikin Royal Secret Service sun koma aiki kuma sun haɗu da kyakkyawan Ofelia Bullet, wani hali da Olga Kirilenko ta buga.
A halin yanzu, Firayim Minista ya fada cikin mummunan tasirin wani mai karfin fasaha mai karfin gaske wanda ke ikirarin cewa zai iya magance matsalolin kwamfuta na Burtaniya: Jason Volta mai mugunta, wanda Jake Lacey ya buga.
Inglish da Bow sun fara odyssey na rashin hankali: suna yin kama da masu jiran abinci suna ƙona gidan cin abinci na Faransa; suna yin ɓarna bayan sun yi wa kansu kwarin gwiwa a kan jirgin ruwan Volta na alatu; kuma Inglish ya fara rikici na ainihi lokacin da yake ƙoƙarin amfani da madaidaicin gaskiya don sanin cikin gidan Volta.
An cire duk abin da ke cikin motar don na ƙarshe, amma duk da cewa yana da kyau da kuma sauti, akwai TV na yara a cikin fim ɗin.
Abubuwa masu kyau masu kyau.
