Menene bikin Global Citizen yake nufi, kuma ya yi wani abu don rage talauci?
A wannan Asabar, za a yi bikin Global Citizen a birnin New York, wani biki na shekara-shekara na kiɗa da ke cike da taurari masu tasowa da kuma manufa mai ban sha'awa: kawo ƙarshen talauci.
Yanzu an gudanar da bikin na bakwai, kuma bikin Global Citizen zai ziyarci dubun dubatan mutane da za su zo babban ciyawa a Central Park, ba wai kawai don jin daɗin wasan kwaikwayon sunaye kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Sean Mendes ba, amma kuma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin burin kawar da matsanancin talauci a shekarar 2030.
Bikin Global Citizen, wanda aka fara a shekarar 2012, ci gaba ne na aikin yaki da talauci na duniya, wani rukuni na masu gwagwarmaya na duniya wanda ke fatan kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke yaki da talauci.
Don samun tikiti kyauta don taron (sai dai idan ba sa son biyan tikitin VIP), mahalarta dole ne su cika wasu ayyuka ko ayyuka kamar su ba da gudummawa, aika saƙon imel ga wani shugaban duniya, kiran waya ko wani aiki mai amfani wanda zai taimaka wajen wayar da kan jama'a game da manufar kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya nasarar Global Citizen yake idan ya rage shekaru 12 kafin a kammala?
Shin ra'ayin yin kide kide kyauta hanya ce ta gaske ta shawo kan mutane su nemi su sauke wani abu ko kuwa wani misali ne na "click-activism" - mutane da suke jin cewa suna yin canji ta hanyar sanya hannu kan takarda ta yanar gizo ko aika saƙo a Twitter?
Tun daga 2011, Global Citizen ta ce ta yi rajistar fiye da miliyan 19 na ayyukan masu goyon baya, wadanda suka yi aiki don dalilai daban-daban.
Sun ce waɗannan ayyukan sun taimaka wajen ƙarfafa shugabannin duniya su gabatar da alkawura da tsare-tsare da suka tara fiye da dala biliyan 37 da za su shafi rayuwar mutane biliyan 2.25 har zuwa 2030.
A farkon 2018, kungiyar ta kawo alkawura 390 da sanarwar da suka fito daga ayyukansu, wanda dala biliyan 10 aka riga aka aika ko aka tara.
Ƙungiyar ta kimanta cewa kuɗin da aka tara ya shafi mutane kusan miliyan 649 a dukan duniya.
Wasu daga cikin muhimman alkawuran sune Power of Food, wata kungiya ta masu zuba jari da masu aiwatarwa, dake zaune a Birtaniya, wadanda suka sadaukar da kansu wajen "taimakawa yara su cika burinsu", wanda ya yi alkawarin samar da dala miliyan 35 ga Rwanda domin taimakawa wajen magance rashin abinci mai gina jiki a kasar bayan ya samu sakonni 4,700 a shafin Twitter daga Global Citizens.
"Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu bayar da agaji, gwamnatocin kasa da kuma 'yan kasa na duniya kamar ku, za mu iya kawo rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki a tarihi", in ji jakadan abinci na kasar, Tracy Ullman, a gaban jama'a a wani taron raye-raye a London a watan Afrilu na shekarar 2018.
Kungiyar ta kuma ce an dauki ayyuka sama da 5,000 da suka shafi kira don inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga mata da yara a Burtaniya, gwamnatin ta sanar da kudade ga aikin, Power of Food, wanda zai shafi mata da yara miliyan 5 tare da maganganun abinci mai gina jiki.
A amsa ga tambayar da ake yawan yi a shafin su na yanar gizo, "Me ya sa kuke ganin za ku iya kawo karshen talauci?"
Daga Global Citizen suka amsa: "Zai zama hanya mai tsawo da wahala - ba za mu taɓa yin nasara ba.
Amma kamar manyan ƙungiyoyin farar hula da na 'yanci da suka gabata, za mu yi nasara, domin tare muna da ƙarfi.
Janet Jackson, Weekend, Sean Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Mona na daga cikin masu fasahar da za su yi waka a bikin na bana a New York, wanda Deborah-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman za su shirya.
Amurka na iya amfani da rundunar sojin ruwanta wajen hana fitar da makamashin Rasha
Washington na iya "yin amfani da rundunar sojin ruwa idan ya zama dole" don hana makamashin Rasha zuwa kasuwannin da suka hada da Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka Ryan Zinke, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ta ruwaito.
A cewar Zinki, shigar Rasha cikin Syria - wato, inda take aiki bisa gayyatar wata gwamnati mai halal - wata hujja ce ta gano sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
"Ina ganin dalilin da ya sa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne domin su yi kasuwanci da makamashi, kamar yadda suke yi a gabashin Turai, kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
Kuma a cewar jami'in gwamnati, akwai hanyoyin magance wannan.
"Amurka tana da ikon, tare da rundunar sojin ruwanmu, ta tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin teku za su kasance a bude kuma idan ya zama dole ta hanyar toshewa, ta hana makamashin su zuwa kasuwa", in ji shi.
Zincki ya yi magana ne a wani taron da kungiyar masu amfani da makamashi ta shirya, kungiyar da ba ta cin riba ba ce wacce ke bayyana kanta a matsayin "muryar masu amfani da makamashi" a Amurka.
Ya ci gaba da kwatanta yadda Washington ke bi da Rasha da Iran, yana mai cewa, yana da tasiri iri ɗaya.
"Zaɓin tattalin arziki na Iran da Rasha shine, mafi yawa ko žasa, don ƙarawa da maye gurbin man fetur", in ji shi, yayin da yake magana game da Rasha a matsayin "wani abu mara kyau" tare da tattalin arziƙin man fetur.
Sanarwar ta biyo bayan da gwamnatin Trump ta fara aikin bunkasa fitar da iskar gas zuwa Turai, inda ta maye gurbin Rasha, wadda ta fi masu amfani da ita kudin da ake bukata.
Don haka, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da shugaban Amurka Donald Trump, suna kokarin shawo kan Jamus ta janye daga aikin samar da iskar gas na Nordtek 2, wanda Trump ya ce ya mayar da Berlin "bautar Moscow".
