Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo yana shirin fara sabon intanet domin kalubalanci Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo ya fara kasuwanci da ke da'awar cewa zai iya gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin da aka yi wa wannan ƙwararren masanin fasaha, Inrapts, kamfani ne da aka gina a kan hanyar buɗe tushen Solid na Berners-Lee.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su da kuma waɗanne mutane za su iya samun damar waɗanne bayanai.
A wata hira ta musamman da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi wa dariya cewa burin Inrupt shi ne "mulkin duniya".
"Dole ne mu yi shi yanzu", in ji shi game da kasuwancin farawa.
"Yanzu ne lokacin tarihi".
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar nasu "shagon yanar gizo" ko POD don gajeren lokaci.
Za ka iya samun jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin abubuwan da za a yi, kalandar, laburaren waƙa, da kuma wasu kayan aiki na sana'a da na sirri.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify suna cikin wannan mai bincike a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke na musamman game da ajiyar bayanan sirri na Intanet shi ne, yana da kawai a kan mai amfani wanda ke da damar zuwa wani nau'in bayanai.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan "karfafa mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar InRapt, a cewar Shugaba John Bruce, ita ce kamfanin ya samar da albarkatu, tsari da kuma ƙwarewar da ta dace don Solid ya kasance ga kowa.
Kamfanin a halin yanzu ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu haɓaka shirye-shirye tare da kwangilar aiki a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen sa kai.
Farawa daga wannan makon, masu fasahar kere-kere a duniya zasu iya gina nasu aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ake samu a shafin yanar gizon InRapt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba su tattauna da Facebook da Google ba game da ko za su yi cikakken sauyi inda tsarin kasuwancin su ya lalace baki daya.
Ba ma neman izininsu.
A cikin wani sakon da aka wallafa a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa manufar Inraptt ita ce samar da wutar lantarki da kuma tsarin halittu na kasuwanci wanda zai taimaka wajen kare mutunci da ingancin sabuwar hanyar sadarwa da aka gina bisa Solid.
A 1994, Berners-Lee ya sake fasalin Intanet ta hanyar kafa Cibiyar Sadarwar Yanar Gizo ta Massachusetts.
A kwanan nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai magana da yawun masu fafutuka a batun tsaka tsaki na intanet.
Ko da a lokacin da aka fara tare da InRapt, Berners-Lee zai kasance wanda ya kafa kuma darektan Consortium na World Wide Web, Gidauniyar Intanet da Cibiyar Bayanai ta Bude.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da sabuwar zamanin Intanet", in ji Berners-Lee.
