Wani mutum da aka harbe da bindiga a filin jirgin sama a Ilfracombe
Wani mutum ya samu harbi da bindiga a kan hanyarsa ta dawowa gida daga wani biki.
Wanda aka kashe a cikin shekara 40 yana zaune a unguwar Oxford Grove da ke Ilfracombe lokacin da aka harbe shi a cikin kirji, ciki da hannu.
Jami'an 'yan sanda sun bayyana harbin, wanda ya faru da misalin karfe 02:30 BST (lokacin bazara na Burtaniya) a matsayin "aikin da ba a saba gani ba".
Wanda aka kashe bai ga wanda ya kai masa hari ba.
Raunin da ya yi bai yi barazanar rai ba kuma 'yan sanda sun yi kira ga shaidu su taimaka.
Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
A kalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a sakamakon girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palau na Indonesia ranar Juma'a, kamar yadda jami'ai suka ce, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Saboda katsewar sadarwa, masu ba da agaji ba za su iya samun bayanai daga gundumar Donggala ba, yankin arewacin Palu wanda ya fi kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5.
An kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga garin Palu bayan hatsarin.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palau da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu shine babban birnin lardin Central Sulawesi, wanda ke kan iyakar bakin tekun a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan mutane 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
An yi bikin cika shekara 40 da haihuwar birnin a lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da kuma tsunami suka addabe shi.
Donggala gundumar da ke da nisan fiye da kilomita 300 (180 miles) a gabar tekun arewa maso yamma na tsibirin Sulawesi.
Gundumar, wacce ke wakiltar yanki na gudanarwa a cikin lardi, a cikin 2017 tana da ƙididdigar yawan mutane 299,200.
Kamun kifi da noma sune manyan hanyoyin samun kudin shiga ga tattalin arzikin lardin na Tsakiya Sulawesi, musamman a yankin Dongola na bakin teku.
Ruwa na nickel ma muhimmin aiki ne a lardin, amma galibi yana da maida hankali ne a Morava, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesiya ta ce a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, an yi wa Palu da Donggala tsunami sau da yawa.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami kuma ya afka yammacin Donggala a shekara ta 1996, inda mutane tara suka mutu.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake kira Pacific Ring of Fire kuma tana yawan fuskantar girgizar ƙasa.
Wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a cikin 'yan shekarun nan su ne:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya afkawa kasashe 14, inda ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su mazauna Aceh ne.
2005: An yi wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane suka mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke gabar Sumatra.
2006: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudu maso gabashin Java, tsibirin da ke da yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta jawo tsunami da ya halaka gaɓar tekun kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.6 ta afkawa wani yanki kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Yammacin Sumatra.
Fiye da mutane 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai, kusa da Sumatra, ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa, kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa mai zurfin gaske ta afkawa gundumar Pidi Jaya a Aceh, inda ta haifar da bala'i da fargaba saboda ta tunatar da mutane game da mummunar girgizar kasa da tsunami a shekarar 2004.
A wannan lokacin, girgizar ƙasar ba ta jawo tsunami ba, amma sama da mutane 100 ne suka mutu domin gine-gine da suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta halaka dubban gine-gine kuma ta sa dubban masu yawon buɗe ido suka makale na ɗan lokaci.
An Kama Ɗan Sara Palin da Ya Fi Dukansu Tsanani a Kan Laifin Yin Zagi a Gida
An kama Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma dan takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa Sarah Palin bisa zargin kai hari.
Palin, mai shekara 29, daga Vasilla, Alaska, an kama shi ne bisa zargin cin zarafin cikin gida, tsoma baki a cikin rahoton cin zarafin cikin gida, da kuma adawa da kamawa, a cewar rahoton da jami'an 'yan sanda a Alaska suka fitar a ranar Asabar.
Rahoton 'yan sanda ya ce sa'ad da wata mata da ta san shi ta yi ƙoƙari ta kira 'yan sanda don ta ba da rahoton laifin da ake zarginsa da shi, sai ya karɓe wayar.
