A watan Janairun 2016, an tuhume shi da hare-haren gida, tsangwama a cikin rahoton laifin cin zarafin cikin gida, da kuma mallakar makami a ƙarƙashin tasirin barasa dangane da lamarin.
Budurwarsa ta ce ya buge ta a fuska.
