Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya na neman hukuncin kisa kan wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addancin New York.
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya a birnin New York na neman a yanke wa Saifullo Saif, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci da ya kashe mutane takwas a birnin New York hukuncin kisa, hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa a jihar ba tun shekarar 1953.
Saipow, mai shekara 30, a watan Oktoba ya yi zargin cewa ya yi amfani da motar haya daga Home Depot don kai hari kan hanyar keke a kan titin West Side a Manhattan da ke ƙasa kuma ya kori masu tafiya da ƙafa da masu hawan keke da suka same shi a hanyarsa.
Don a ba da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su bukaci a tabbatar da cewa Saif ya yi kisan da gangan ga wadanda aka kashe da kuma cewa ya yi wa wasu da dama rauni, a cewar sanarwar da aka bayar a kotun da ke kula da shari'ar da ke yankin kudancin birnin New York.
Bisa ga takardun kotu akwai yiwuwar yanke hukuncin kisa bisa ga waɗannan dalilai biyu na tuhumar.
Makonni bayan harin, babban kotun tarayya ta gurfanar da Saif a kan zarge-zarge 22, ciki har da zarge-zarge takwas na kisan kai don manufar cin hanci da rashawa, wanda ake amfani da shi a lokuta da yawa a cikin masu gabatar da kara na tarayya, da kuma tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Aikin harin ya bukaci "shirye-shirye da kuma tunani sosai", in ji masu gabatar da kara, inda suka bayyana yadda Saif ya aikata harin a matsayin "mai tsanani, mai tsanani da kuma lalata".
"Saipul Habibulevich Saipow ya yi wa iyalan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleaves, Anne-Laure Decatt, Darren Drake, Ariel Earle, Hernan Ferrucci, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucho rauni, lalacewa da kuma asarar abokai", in ji sanarwar da gwamnatin kasar ta yi.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda suka mutu 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekara goma ke nan da aka yi shari'ar kisa a Kudancin New York.
Wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes an yanke masa hukuncin kisa kan masu sayar da miyagun kwayoyi guda biyu, amma daga karshe aka yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar shekarar 2009.
A shekarar 1953 ne aka kashe Yuliya da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan an yanke musu hukuncin laifin yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An yanke musu hukuncin kisa ta wurin kujerar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, wanda aka haifa a Uzbekistan, bai nuna nadama ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun kotu.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa yana jin daɗi game da abin da ya yi.
A cewar tuhumar, Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa ya samu kwarin gwiwa wajen kai harin ne bayan ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa.
'Yan sanda sun kuma ce ya nemi a saka tutar ISIS a dakin sa na asibiti.
