David Patton, daya daga cikin masu kare hakkin jama'a na tarayya da ke wakiltar Saif ya ce sun "yi matukar takaici" da hukuncin da mai gabatar da kara ya yanke.
"Mun yi imanin cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar hukuncin daurin rai da rai ba tare da damar sakewa ba zai kara ci gaba da raunin da wannan lamarin ya haifar ga duk wanda ke cikin lamarin", in ji Patton.
