Syria ta ce tana shirye don dawo da 'yan gudun hijirar da son rai, kuma tana kokarin taimakawa wajen sake gina kasar da aka lalata ta sakamakon tsawon yakin da aka shafe sama da shekaru bakwai.
A jawabinsa ga babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan harkokin wajen kasar Walid al-Mu'alim ya ce yanayin kasar na inganta.
"Yau, yanayin da ake ciki a kan kasa ya fi kwanciyar hankali da tsaro, saboda ci gaban da aka samu a yaki da ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da gyara wuraren da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata domin dawo da al'amuran cikin sauki.
Yanzu an samar da dukkan yanayi don 'yan gudun hijirar su koma ƙasarsu da son ransu, inda suka yi gudun hijira saboda ta'addanci da kuma matakan tattalin arziki da aka saka wa kansu, wanda ya shafi rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa fiye da 'yan Syria miliyan 5.5 ne suka tsere daga kasar tun lokacin da yakin ya fara a shekarar 2011.
An kuma samu karin mutane miliyan shida da ke zaune a kasar da ke bukatar taimakon jin kai.
Al-Mu'alem ya ce gwamnatin Syria ta yi maraba da taimakon da ake bayarwa wajen sake gina kasar da aka lalata.
Amma ya ce ba zai amince da taimakon da aka ba shi ba ko kuma taimakon da kasashen da suka tallafa wa tawayen suka bayar.
Turai ta yi gagarumar nasara a gasar Ryder Cup a Paris
Tawagar Turai ta doke tawagar Amurka a Ryder Cup 2018 da ƙimar ƙarshe ta 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National, a wajen Paris, Faransa.
Amurka ta yi rashin nasara a gasar cin kofin Ryder Cup a Turai sau shida a jere, kuma ba ta lashe kofin Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta dawo da primate bayan da dan kasar Denmark Thomas Bjorn ya jagoranci tawagarsa ta samu maki 14.5 da ake bukata domin cin Amurka.
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson wanda ya sha wahala a gasar, ya buga kwallo a cikin ruwa a kan rami na 16 a kan rami na uku, inda ya rasa daga hannun Francesco Molinari.
Dan wasan golf na Italiya Molinari ya yi fice a dukkan matakai, inda ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasa hudu da suka ci 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a shekarar 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spit ya sha kashi 5-4 a hannun dan wasan da ya fi kowacce a gasar Turai, Torbjörn Olesen na Denmark.
Dustin Johnson, dan wasan da ya fi kowacce a duniya, ya ci Ian Poulter da ci 2 da 1 daga Ingila, wanda zai iya zama wasan karshe da ya buga a gasar Ryder Cup.
Tsohon dan wasan Spain Sergio Garcia, wanda ya halarci gasar Ryder Cup takwas, ya zama dan Turai da ya lashe mafi yawan wasannin gasar tare da cin kwallaye 25.5 a tsawon aikinsa.
