Sabuntawar Red Tide: Rage yawan mutane a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Wani rahoto na Hukumar Kula da Kifi da namun daji ta Florida ya nuna cewa yawan ruwan sama a yankunan Tampa Bay ya ragu.
A cewar Hukumar, an lura da yanayin rashin daidaiton algae a yankin Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier, wanda ke nuna raguwar taro.
Red tide, sakamakon hawan ruwan algae mai launin ja yana da nisan mil 130 a bakin teku daga gundumar Pinellas ta arewa zuwa gundumar Lee ta kudu.
Ana iya ganin ɓangarorin jan ruwa a kusan mil 10 na gabar tekun gundumar Hillsborough, amma duk da haka adadin ya ragu idan aka kwatanta da na makon da ya gabata.
An kuma samu wani jan ruwa a gundumar Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata an samu irin wadannan abubuwan: matsakaitan abubuwa a ko a gabar tekun Pinellas County, low to high a gabar tekun Hillsborough County, na kowa zuwa high a ko a gabar tekun Sarasota County, na kowa zuwa matsakaici a Charlotte County, na kowa zuwa high a ko a gabar tekun Lee County, da kuma low a Coolier County.
An ci gaba da samun ciwon iska a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier.
Babu rahoton cutar numfashi a arewa maso yammacin Florida a makon da ya gabata.
